## 命名约定

- **目录名**: kebab-case (`sponsor-vultr-worker/`)
- **文件名**: 与目录一致
- **函数名**: camelCase (TS) / snake_case (Python)
- **环境变量**: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`，sponsor-prefixed (`VULTR_API_KEY`)
- **分支名**: `<owner>/<feat-name>`（如 `duan/sponsor-vultr-init` / `ryan/frontend-pipeline`）
- **commit prefix**: `feat:` / `fix:` / `chore:` / `wip:`

